# Java / Maven (Quarkus backend).

# Build output. Generated protobuf Java DTOs live under target/generated-sources and are
# regenerated from proto/ on every build, so they are intentionally NOT committed, the
# committed contract artifacts are the Dart/TS ones the sync:contracts gate tracks.
target/

# Quarkus
.quarkus/
*.class

# The Maven wrapper (mvnw, mvnw.cmd, .mvn/wrapper/) IS committed, do not ignore it.
